-time interaction, questions, discussions, and support from peers and instructors. Meeting links are posted there, and assignments are announced there, keeping you fully in the loop.\n    *   **WhatsApp:** After each class, a summary is shared in the official CodeCraft WhatsApp group, helping you review and reinforce what you\'ve learned. This continuous engagement keeps you connected and supported.\n\n3.  **Flexible Access to Learning Materials:**\n    *   **Google Meet:** Classes are live via Google Meet, allowing for direct interaction and questions.\n    *   **Lecture Recordings:** Missed a class or want to review a complex topic? No problem! All lecture recordings are available on the CodeCraft website. As a paid member, you\'ll have 24/7 access using your unique "member key," so you can learn at your own pace and revisit concepts whenever you need to.\n\n4.  **Practical, Hands-on Experience:** We believe in learning by doing! Assignments are a core part of the CodeCraft experience, providing you with practical challenges to apply what you\'ve learned. This hands-o', 'mentions': [], 'mention_roles': [], 'attachments': [], 'embeds': [], 'timestamp': '2026-04-21T21:28:45.187000+00:00', 'edited_timestamp': None, 'flags': 0, 'components': [], 'id': '1496261434538197136', 'channel_id': '1494248822715584565', 'author': {'id': '1495823027798282471', 'username': 'CodeCraftBot', 'avatar': 'a1b87579232f9ec6190d90437a1f4a0b', 'discriminator': '2853', 'public_flags': 0, 'flags': 0, 'bot': True, 'banner': None, 'accent_color': None, 'global_name': None, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'collectibles': None, 'display_name_styles': None, 'banner_color': None, 'clan': None, 'primary_guild': None}, 'pinned': False, 'mention_everyone': False, 'tts': False}, {'type': 0, 'content': 'Hi, could you convince me why I should stay in CodeCraft?', 'mentions': [], 'mention_roles': [], 'attachments': [], 'embeds': [], 'timestamp': '2026-04-21T21:28:35.818000+00:00', 'edited_timestamp': Non